  Locus:
    Page: 423
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - Service
---
If you hear that a sick man is in need of hot soup, I counsel you to wake
up from your ecstasy and warm the soup for him. Leave God to serve God;
find Him and serve Him in His members; you will lose nothing by the change.
